text: Laurie Brett (born 28 March 1969) is a Scottish actress. She is best known for playing the roles of Jane Beale in the BBC soap opera EastEnders (2004–2012, 2014–2017), and Christine Mulgrew in the BBC school-based drama series Waterloo Road (2012–2015). ==Other websites== * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Scottish television actors Category:People from South Lanarkshire
